e','#e74c3c','legal notices\n法律通知：一种正式的通知或警告，通常由律师或法院发出，以告知某人或某些人有关法律事宜的信息。','2026-06-25 14:13:15'),('mqvs69502rooqu','f05fddb8-0838-425c-8cf0-de85a8907ba3',2,115,399,' In October the current administration unveiled an \"international pricing index\" that would link the prices paid for a number of expensive drugs purchased by Medicare, a giant government health-care plan for the aged, to lower prices paid for those same drugs by other rich countries.','sentence','#2980b9','今年10月，本届政府公布了一项「国际价格指数」计划，拟将面向老年人的政府大型医保计划「联邦医疗保险」（Medicare）采购的多款昂贵药品的价格，与其他富裕国家同类药品的较低价格挂钩。','2026-06-27 03:08:43'),('mqvsx0f2zc3h8k','f05fddb8-0838-425c-8cf0-de85a8907ba3',3,518,530,'confidential','highlight','#FFEB3B','confidential\n英 / ˌkɒnfɪˈdenʃ(ə)l /\n美 / ˌkɑːnfɪˈdenʃ(ə)l /\nadj. 机密的，保密的；（言谈举止）神秘的，隐秘的；受信任的，委以机密的','2026-06-27 03:29:32'),('mqvx29cp65kc51','f05fddb8-0838-425c-8cf0-de85a8907ba3',4,83,231,' Momentum is building for American regulators to catch up with Europe in promoting \"biosimilars\", which are common approximations of patented drugs.','sentence','#2980b9','美国监管机构正加速追赶欧洲步伐，推动「生物类似药」（biosimilars，专利药的通用仿制版本）发展的势头日益强劲。','2026-06-27 05:25:35'),('mqvxbzoymm4tgx','f05fddb8-0838-425c-8cf0-de85a8907ba3',4,335,341,'milked','underline','#e74c3c','“milk”在此处为动词，是形象化用法，意为“榨取（利益）；从……中牟利”，常用结构“milk sth. for all it\'s worth”表示“充分利用某物获利”，此处“be milked”为其被动形式）','2026-06-27 05:33:09'),('mqvxq1y37nyxxv','f05fddb8-0838-425c-8cf0-de85a8907ba3',5,77,303,' Observing that at no time in his career has he seen such commitment to tackling drug pricing, insists Steve Miller, the chief clinical officer of Cigna Express Scripts, a recent union of a big insurance company and a big PBM.','sentence','#2980b9','大型保险公司与大型药房福利管理机构的近期联合体「信诺快捷药方」（Cigna Express Scripts）的首席临床官史蒂夫·米勒坚称，在其职业生涯中，从未见过如此坚定的解决药价问题的决心。','2026-06-27 05:44:05'),('mqvxuw7mkjf1tw','f05fddb8-0838-425c-8cf0-de85a8907ba3',1,225,229,'tame','highlight','#FFEB3B','tame\n英 / teɪm /\n美 / teɪm /\nadj. 驯服的，不怕人的；平淡无奇的，枯燥乏味的；听使唤的，温顺的；&lt;美&gt; （植物）经栽培的；（土地）经开垦的\nv. 驯化，驯服；制服，控制；开垦，开辟；使变得平淡\n【名】 （Tame）（捷）塔梅（人名）','2026-06-27 05:47:51'),('mqw05tno1s0rla','f05fddb8-0838-425c-8cf0-de85a8907ba3',3,258,264,'rebate','highlight','#FFEB3B','rebate\n英 / ˈriːbeɪt /\n美 / ˈriːbeɪt /\nv. 退还（部分付款）；扣除；在（木块）上开槽口；用槽口衔接（木块）\nn. 退还款；折扣；（木块的）槽口；返还部分\nn. （Rebate）（印）雷瓦特（人名）','2026-06-27 06:52:20'),('mqw476o8tqyhf4','f05fddb8-0838-425c-8cf0-de85a8907ba3',3,121,133,'a handful of','underline','#e74c3c','a handful of\n一把；一小撮；少量的','2026-06-27 08:45:22'),('mqw4agxkha2tvi','f05fddb8-0838-425c-8cf0-de85a8907ba3',3,638,652,'hailed this as','underline','#e74c3c','“hail sth. as...”是固定搭配，意为“称赞某事物为……','2026-06-27 08:47:55'),('mqx9zqxl7h2wv6','3ad67edd-1573-4aff-ad4e-6964f2da8a70',1,268,278,'come under','underline','#e74c3c','come under\n受到（某事物）的影响、控制或影响：指某事物受到某种外部力量、条件或影响的作用。\n属于（某一类别或组别）：用于指明某事物所属的类别或组别。','2026-06-28 04:15:19'),('mqxlhxdc8nmqqs','3ad67edd-1573-4aff-ad4e-6964f2da8a70',2,336,358,'real estate profession','underline','#e74c3c','real estate profession\n房地产行业','2026-06-28 09:37:23'),('mqxlid3hltlkmp','3ad67edd-1573-4aff-ad4e-6964f2da8a70',2,325,331,'covers','underline','#e74c3c','“cover”在此处意为“适用于；涵盖；涉及”；','2026-06-28 09:37:43'),('mqxmn2w3aw8j05','3ad67edd-1573-4aff-ad4e-6964f2da8a70',3,234,243,'directive','highlight','#FFEB3B','directive\n英 / dəˈrektɪv; daɪˈrektɪv /\n美 / dəˈrektɪvˌdaɪˈrektɪv /\nn. 指示；指令\nadj. 指导的；管理的','2026-06-28 10:09:23'),('mqxmyhlvpkpfhn','3ad67edd-1573-4aff-ad4e-6964f2da8a70',3,252,437,' The ruling made mention of a recent case in which Uber was found to be acting as a transport company rather than an information society service leading to tighter regulatory oversight.','sentence','#2980b9','裁决中提及近期一起案件——优步（Uber）被认定属于运输公司而非信息社会服务，因而面临更严监管。','2026-06-28 10:18:15'),('mqxo5eoo5mlsax','3ad67edd-1573-4aff-ad4e-6964f2da8a70',4,113,122,'complaint','highlight','#FFEB3B','complaint\n英 / kəmˈpleɪnt /\n美 / kəmˈpleɪnt /\nn. 抱怨，投诉；不满的缘由，抱怨的问题；疾病，不适','2026-06-28 10:51:38'),('mqxo71e8eovrka','3ad67edd-1573-4aff-ad4e-6964f2da8a70',4,103,122,'filed our complaint','underline','#e74c3c','“file a complaint”是法律和商务常用搭配，意为“提交投诉；提起诉讼”；','2026-06-28 10:52:54');
